name: Eye of Ender
description: An eye of ender is a craftable item used to locate strongholds and activate the end portals within them. It is also used to craft an end crystal or an ender chest.

name: Feather

name: Fermented Spider Eye

name: Field Masoned Banner Pattern

name: Fire Charge

name: Firework Rocket

name: Firework Star

name: Fishing Rod

name: Flint

name: Flint and Steel

name: Netherite Boots
description: Netherite boots are the strongest tier of boots available, only obtainable by combining diamond boots, a netherite ingot, and netherite upgrade using a smithing table. Like all netherite armor, these boots provides 10% knockback resistance when worn, and are completely immune to fire and lava, including both worn and item forms.

name: Netherite Chestplate

This chestplate is only obtainable by combining a diamond chestplate, netherite ingot, and netherite upgrade using a smithing table. Like all netherite armor, this chestplate provides 10% knockback resistance when worn, and is completely immune to fire and lava, including both worn and item forms.

name: Netherite Helmet

name: Netherite Hoe

name: Netherite Ingot

Unlike other items, it is immune to being destroyed by fire and lava. They are primarily used to upgrade diamond gear and craft lodestones.

name: Netherite Leggings

name: Netherite Shovel
description: A netherite shovel has a mining level of 4 and the highest durability of any shovel. It can be used to hasten the process of breaking dirt, sand, gravel, and other soil blocks, as well as to convert dirt blocks into dirt paths.

name: Netherite Sword
